Sentencas: The development of highly efficient and robust cathodes is crucial for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFC).
Titulo: A SrCo0.9Ta0.1O3-δ derived medium-entropy cathode with superior CO2 poisoning tolerance for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Perovskite type SrCo0.9Ta0.1O3-delta (SCT91) is a promising cathode but its instability against CO2 limits the practical application.
Titulo: A SrCo0.9Ta0.1O3-δ derived medium-entropy cathode with superior CO2 poisoning tolerance for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this work, a new medium-entropy SrCo0.5Fe0.2Ti0.1Ta0.1Nb0.1O3-delta (SCFTTN52111) cathode is designed and evaluated.
Titulo: A SrCo0.9Ta0.1O3-δ derived medium-entropy cathode with superior CO2 poisoning tolerance for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The effect of configuration entropy on electrical conductivity, physical and electrochemical properties are studied in detail.
Titulo: A SrCo0.9Ta0.1O3-δ derived medium-entropy cathode with superior CO2 poisoning tolerance for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The SCFTTN52111 cathode exhibits a lower polarization resistance of 0.033 Omega cm(2) at 700 degrees C, superior to 0.040 Omega cm(2) of SCT91 parent.
Titulo: A SrCo0.9Ta0.1O3-δ derived medium-entropy cathode with superior CO2 poisoning tolerance for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The higher oxygen reduction activity is attributed to its larger surface exchange coefficient and smaller particle size.
Titulo: A SrCo0.9Ta0.1O3-δ derived medium-entropy cathode with superior CO2 poisoning tolerance for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: More importantly, SCFTTN52111 displays outstanding stability and high CO2 tolerance, due to a more negative value of average metal-oxygen bond energy and significantly reduced surface Sr segregation.
Titulo: A SrCo0.9Ta0.1O3-δ derived medium-entropy cathode with superior CO2 poisoning tolerance for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Our study provides a feasible and effective entropy engineering approach to design high-active and durable cathode materials for SOFCs.
Titulo: A SrCo0.9Ta0.1O3-δ derived medium-entropy cathode with superior CO2 poisoning tolerance for solid oxide fuel cells
